				<td colspan="2"><span>Stats dont exactly matter ( at least in my opinion) to a bard.  You spend a majority of your time kiting.  You dont really need any of the stats., except maybe intelligence to help a little with your mana pool when you start swarm kiting. If a mob cant touch you, then you dont really need HP, or the ability to dodge their attacks.  if your not going to stand toe to toe you dont really need to be able to hit them hard, or dodge their attacks.</span></td>
