All stats can eventually be worked up with gear, we all can agree on that.  However, casters fizzles depend on their skill in each of the 4 areas, not on their stats.  Our missed notes are based on our skill plus our charisma (as shown in the parsings done that are somewhere on the boards) with Dex being a bit of a factor as well.  Also our charisma affects our ability to mez, charm, and lull.
<br />

